name: Supernova Jim
description: This is the "Blue/Orange" version of my "Supernova Jim" character. The original painting was made with acrylic paint for the abstract background and all the black lines were done with an acrylic ink. This is a 1/1, which means only one of these will be minted to the blockchain. There are 3 different color versions available, but only 1 of each, so they are totally unique originals. I hope you enjoy it! Twitter: @jeffclaassen - Instagram: @jeffclaassen
